Add support for coverage exclusion comments (Richard Bradley)\n\n##### 8 March 2014 - 0.95.9\n* SBT plugin import issue fixed\n* Fixed windows line ending issues\n* Use relative href for source view\n* Add support for exclude by file name\n\n##### 12th Jan 2014 - 0.95.7\n* Fixed bug with return value in pattern match\n* Improved support for classname excludes\n* Fixed spurious trailing green line breaks\n\n##### 5th Jan 2014 - 0.95.3\n* Fixed support for for comprehensions. \n* Optimzed support for nested method calls.\n* Fixed exclude package bug\n* Now supports nested packages\n\n##### 9th Dec 2013 - 0.95.0\n* First stable release.\n\n succeeded in 171ms:\ncurl: (22) The requested URL returned error: 404\n\nexec\n/usr/bin/bash -lc 'git diff -- build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.scoverage-scalac-scoverage-plugin-1.1.1.json' in /home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge2/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3600-9e97be3e\n succeeded in 0ms:\nexec\n/usr/bin/bash -lc \"curl -fsSL https://api.github.com/repos/scoverage/scalac-scoverage-plugin/git/trees/1.1.1?recursive=1 | rg '\\\"path\\\": \\\"scalac-scoverage-plugin/src/main' | head -20\" in /home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge2/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3600-9e97be3e\ndiff --git a/build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.scoverage-scalac-scoverage-plugin-1.1.1.json b/build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.scoverage-scalac-scoverage-plugin-1.1.1.json\nindex 55d8ad71542311646f960ead259b5ce4a8df0df5..1c22cfccf3fe115c47f9c5ffa4a4de5f4da6131d\n--- a/build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.scoverage-scalac-scoverage-plugin-1.1.1.json\n+++ b/build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.scoverage-scalac-scoverage-plugin-1.1.1.json\n@@ -1,3 +1,12 @@\n {\n-  \"coordinates\" : \"org.scoverage:scalac-scoverage-plugin:1.1.1\"\n+  \"coordinates\" : \"org.scoverage:scalac-scoverage-plugin:1.1.1\",\n+  \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/scoverage/scala